quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,6,"Thalika bi-anna Allaha huwa alhaqquwaannahu yuhyee almawta waannahu AAala kullishay-in qadeer"
  22,7,"Waanna assaAAata atiyatunla rayba feeha waanna Allaha yabAAathu manfee alquboor"
  22,8,"Wamina annasi man yujadilufee Allahi bighayri AAilmin wala hudan walakitabin muneer"
  22,9,"Thaniya AAitfihi liyudillaAAan sabeeli Allahi lahu fee addunyakhizyun wanutheequhu yawma alqiyamati AAathabaalhareeq"
  22,10,"Thalika bima qaddamat yadakawaanna Allaha laysa bithallaminlilAAabeed"
  22,11,"Wamina annasi man yaAAbuduAllaha AAala harfin fa-in asabahukhayrun itmaanna bihi wa-in asabat-hu fitnatuninqalaba AAala wajhihi khasira addunya wal-akhiratathalika huwa alkhusranu almubeen"
  22,12,"YadAAoo min dooni Allahi ma layadurruhu wama la yanfaAAuhu thalikahuwa addalalu albaAAeed"
  22,13,"YadAAoo laman darruhu aqrabu minnafAAihi labi/sa almawla walabi/sa alAAasheer"
  22,14,"Inna Allaha yudkhilu allatheenaamanoo waAAamiloo assalihati jannatintajree min tahtiha al-anharu inna AllahayafAAalu ma yureed"
  22,15,"Man kana yathunnu anlan yansurahu Allahu fee addunya wal-akhiratifalyamdud bisababin ila assama-i thummaliyaqtaAA falyanthur hal yuthhibannakayduhu ma yagheeth"
